12. Additional information at the candidate's discretion, such as evidence of professional or research
activities related to the subject of the postgraduate programme, etc.
13. Single-page photocopy of both sides of the ID card or Passport.
14. A recent photo.
Evaluation process
The evaluation of the candidates and the selection of the admitted ones is based on the following criteria and
